tables.table_schema: CREATE TABLE transactions ( transaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY, amount DECIMAL(10, 2), transaction_type VARCHAR(20), transaction_date TIMESTAMP )
CREATE TABLE customers ( customer_id INT PRIMARY KEY, first_name VARCHAR(50), last_name VARCHAR(50), email VARCHAR(100) )
CREATE TABLE products ( product_id INT PRIMARY KEY, product_name VARCHAR(50), price DECIMAL(10, 2), stock_quantity INT )
CREATE TABLE transaction_history ( history_id INT PRIMARY KEY, transaction_id INT, customer_id INT, product_id INT, transaction_date TIMESTAMP )

CREATE TABLE transactions (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    transaction_id UUID NOT NULL,
    amount DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    transaction_date TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    description TEXT
);
